      "note": "digest",
      "abstract": "AN ACT relating to taxes on electricity production; amending the tax on the production of electricity from wind resources to include a tax on the production of electricity from solar and nuclear generating resources; making conforming amendments; repealing the existing tax on electricity produced from nuclear reactors; and providing for an effective date."
    }
